"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/92131","Cabinet Office","false","2014-10-14","<p>The Cabinet Office, in line with government policy, has begun the transition towards releasing records when they are 20 years old. The Department is on target to complete this process by 2022 by delivering two years’ worth of government records to the National Archives each year.</p><p>Approximately 20 members of staff are engaged in some capacity to ensure and maintain this progress.</p><p> </p>","Horsham","Mr Francis Maude",,"2014-10-14T07:03:17.1332742Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/92131/answer","Biography information for Lord Maude of Horsham","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/92131/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/92131/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2014-09-26","Public Records","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, what targets have been set for the release of his Department's material to the National Archives; what progress has been made in meeting those targets; and how many staff in his Department are engaged in reviewing records for that purpose.","false","Biography information for Lord Beith","Berwick-upon-Tweed","Sir Alan Beith","209605"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/92132","Cabinet Office","false","2014-10-17","<p>Since 2010, Community Organisers have worked in over 400 neighbourhoods across England. Of the 551 Senior Community Organisers recruited and trained through the Community Organisers programme to date, 63 have worked in Yorkshire and the Humber. Organisers do not necessarily work where they live.</p><p> </p>","Reading East","Mr Rob Wilson",,"2014-10-17T08:04:11.1828766Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/92132/answer","Biography information for Mr Rob Wilson","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/92132/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/92132/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2014-09-26","Community Development: Barnsley","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, how many Big Society community organisers living in Barnsley East constituency have been trained to date.","false","Biography information for Michael Dugher","Barnsley East","Michael Dugher","209560"
