"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/92137","HM Treasury","false","2014-10-14","<p>The Treasury is implementing the Civil Service Employee Policy Performance Management System in 2014-15, so the data requested is not available for 2013-14.</p>","South Northamptonshire","Andrea Leadsom",,"2014-10-14T15:35:50.110282Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/92137/answer","Biography information for Andrea Leadsom","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/92137/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/92137/answer",,,,,"14","Treasury","CaTreasury","2014-09-26","Performance Appraisal","1","House of Commons","To ask Mr Chancellor of the Exchequer, how many officials in his Department completed the Civil Service Employment Policy Performance Management System in 2013-14; how many and what proportion of those officials received the (a) exceeded, (b) met and (c) must improve performance mark; and how many and what proportion (i) did and (ii) did not qualify for a bonus under that process.","false","Biography information for John Healey","Wentworth and Dearne","John Healey","209661"
